<p>Your website is more than a digital brochure. It is a ranking asset. Most restaurant websites fail at basic on-page SEO because they prioritize aesthetics over structure.</p>
<h3>Create Dedicated Pages for Key Topics</h3>
<p>Do not put everything on your homepage. Create separate pages for:</p>
